                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No.312.11/1354A.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to <gloss
                            type="to">American Consular Officers in Mexico</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegrams.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-04-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 23, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Department’s instructions of November 25, 1912. Prepare a supplementary report,
                    bringing up to date the general report made by you in compliance with those
                    instructions.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
